**********multiselect***********

1)features:
        -Search within available options 	
	-Displaying counts of selected and available items
	-Select All / Deselect All Buttons
	-Dragging items from the available list to the selected list directly.

2)use :
	load library in controller
	---------------------------------------
	$this->load->library('multiselect');
	---------------------------------------

	method call in smarty
	---------------------------------------
	<%$this->multiselect->display()%>
	---------------------------------------

	note:
		dropdown should have class multiselect and attribute multiple
		
		eg:<%$this->dropdown->display("vCountry","countries[]","class='multiselect' multiple ")%>

 
